</div></div><div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp49074848-solution"><a class="os-number" href="7-exercises#fs-idp49074848">11</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-solution-container">
<p id="fs-idm21247904">NaCl consists of discrete ions arranged in a crystal lattice, not covalently bonded molecules.</p>
</div></div><div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp119456432-solution"><a class="os-number" href="7-exercises#fs-idp119456432">13</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-solution-container">
<p id="fs-idm92647632">ionic: (b), (d), (e), (g), and (i); covalent: (a), (c), (f), (h), (j), and (k)</p>
</div></div><div data-type="solution" id="fs-idm121789856-solution"><a class="os-number" href="7-exercises#fs-idm121789856">15</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-solution-container">
