<p id="fs-idp205940864">Each bond includes a sharing of electrons between atoms. Two electrons are shared in a single bond; four electrons are shared in a double bond; and six electrons are shared in a triple bond.</p>
</div></div><div data-type="solution" id="fs-idp11428640-solution"><a class="os-number" href="7-exercises#fs-idp11428640">45</a><span class="os-divider">. </span><div class="os-solution-container"><p id="fs-idp22600016">(a)<span data-type="newline"><br/></span>
